Type: Single-page web application (React.js)
Purpose: Showcase AI projects, software skills, and career journey. Highlight transition from mechanical engineering to AI/software development.
Target Audience: Recruiters, potential employers, collaborators in AI/software development.

Goals

Present a clear narrative of Jaime’s background and transition from engineering to AI.

Highlight AI and software projects with demos, screenshots, and technical details.

Provide contact information and GitHub links.

Maintain a clean, modern, minimalist UI with intuitive navigation.

User Stories

As a recruiter, I want to quickly see Jaime’s experience and skills so I can evaluate fit for AI/software roles.

As a visitor, I want to explore Jaime’s AI projects and see demos so I can understand his technical capabilities.

As a collaborator, I want easy access to GitHub repos and contact info so I can connect or view code.

